@CarPredictor_Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5235

### Health Check
GET {{CarPredictor_Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### Get All Manufacturers
GET {{CarPredictor_Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/reference/manufacturers
Accept: application/json

### Get Models for Manufacturer (replace {manufacturerId} with actual ID)
GET {{CarPredictor_Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/reference/manufacturers/1/models
Accept: application/json

### Get Years for Model (replace {modelId} with actual ID)
GET {{CarPredictor_Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/reference/models/1/years
Accept: application/json

###
